window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An arranged marriage to an alien space elf? Yes please!</p> <p>Growing up on modern day Earth, I had no idea I’d been selected from birth to help a dying race save their population. So when a starship abducts me for a royal wedding with galactic consequences, my only option is to help its crew of beautiful officers complete their mission.</p> <p>The catch? I have to protect my gorgeous bride and new allies from an alluring enemy who wants my immunity to a fertility-killing plague for herself, even if it means I have to take command…</p> <p>These are the voyages of Michael Kahn.</p>"; 
